text: Yekaterina Antonyuk (born 1 May 1974) is a Belarusian cross-country skier. She competed in two events at the 1998 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian female cross- country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Belarus Category:Cross-country skiers at the 1998 Winter Olympics Category:People from Magadan Category:Sportspeople from Magadan Oblast
